      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="19340419">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/41360221/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u41360221-14.jpg" alt="zd" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19340419/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19340419/" class="">第245页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/41360221/" class=" " title="zd">zd</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19340419">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“当外界疯狂的时候，你尤其要冷静”这是我面对复杂的情境，觉得无法自拔时，必须遵守的规则。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19340419/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-07-01 09:35</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                “当外界疯狂的时候，你尤其要冷静”这是我面对复杂的情境，觉得无法自拔时，必须遵守的规则。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
